| Original | CTRL (...)+ ALT [24] | 101.55 ns |   1.790 ns |    1.587 ns | 0.0224 |       2,662 B |         376 B |
| PR__EDIT | CTRL (...)+ ALT [24] |  34.68 ns |   0.218 ns |    0.182 ns |      - |       1,891 B |             - |

